Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:15.22,jinggao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}翻译：Rcat；校对：小光头；后期：zipwinmax；繁体化：黑羽侖人。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:51.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}張りつめた空気が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:56.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}高まる鼓動広がってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:01:03.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深く息吸い込んだなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.53,0:01:08.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう前しか見えないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:13.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰も代わる事出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:16.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私しか歩けない道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:19.28,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その涙も全て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:22.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}輝きはじめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:27.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だから思いきり振り上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.32,0:01:30.13,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}手のひらに宿る{\fs26}POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:32.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}迷わずにまっすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:35.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}明日へと行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:39.17,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ほんのまばたきの瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:42.12,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}叶えるよ夢の{\fs26}STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:44.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}儚くて遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:47.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}諦めないわいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:49.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私だけの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.85,0:01:54.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)\fs26}BAMBOOBEAT{\r}を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:51.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}喜欢着紧张的空气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:56.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}兴奋起来走向更广阔的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:01:03.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深呼一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.53,0:01:08.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只专注于眼前的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:13.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}谁都无法替代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:16.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只有我才能前进的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:19.28,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}连同那份泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:22.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}全部开始闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:27.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因此将宿于手中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.32,0:01:30.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}尽情挥扬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:32.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果断地  径直地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:35.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}向着明天全力进发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:39.17,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在转瞬即逝之间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:42.12,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}实现那梦中的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:44.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}无论它多么虚幻和遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:47.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也绝不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:49.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}和仅属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.85,0:01:54.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}竹剑节奏响彻永远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:07.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第25话\N剑道和剑道所带来的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这要怎么去啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你不清楚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次不是也来过么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.35,0:02:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是十多年前的事情了！我怎么记得住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  就是那辆公车  我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加比赛的人好多啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为比赛规模很大嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道的味道可是越来越浓了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说那么大声  小心被别人误会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠你紧张吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:02:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠在比赛前竟然会紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论何时何地我都会支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都…疼…疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点疼…小…都都？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了勇次…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去登记吧  这里人很多  小心别走散
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有人没有开打就先想着输啊  白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起以前了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里禁烟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看  这不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的学生呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去领个人战的参赛表了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈你町户高的学生呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次不参加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带另一边的学生来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来你是兼职嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边写上你的名字和学校名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了阅读注意事项
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想的话  这次我们全部参加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果赢下去的话总会在哪里碰头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  结果还是要和小珠比对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能一路赢下来的话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  没干劲？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  以前就在这么想了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在光想想能参加这样的大赛我就热血沸腾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是对手谁我们都要全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是高中剑道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！小聪莉你好有干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去那边排队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早感觉到了  我说你也差不多放弃吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了多少遍了  你是赶不上我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确  这话听得我耳朵生茧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊  即使赶不上你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也已经紧跟在你身后了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果总算解决了啊  上次那个男生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧  反正就是那么回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你是听谁说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我你在我们学校认识的人有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吉川老师吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是对方打电话过来的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候告诉她电话的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  你听着…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下手好快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了！完全不是你想的那样啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来到底怎么样  顺利压下来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧  总之学校只是想要一个责任人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的部团活动真是愉快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一直被骂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  在这里打赢前辈倒是很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是我的污点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找时候咱们来比一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了拿注意事项单哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿新的来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么猫呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道就是全部二十五个场景只出现过一次的灰猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像似乎仿佛是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说「不管是对手是谁」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这一开始就和小珠对上也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她变得更强了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点对不住东
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但今天的小珠状态非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样继续下去的话  在第五战就能和铃木凛对上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是对她的时候能不能发挥出特训的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一回战就对上我  你的运气还真是糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头胜是你的话可是我的幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论武运还是男运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像做梦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都竟然会来我家～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是喜欢才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在连续进攻的时候姿势有抖动一下的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以拿不到有效打击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美  你有录像吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这录像里的小都在我来看也还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯莉她原本是二刀流
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打手部的话一定会被挡开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之取一本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖延时间在对方漏出破绽的一瞬间取得一本的话还是有可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹部有效
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破绽…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹——！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹部有效
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段君  宫崎同学她怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:09:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都的首次胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！虽然我输了但…好棒好棒好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜利…就是这样的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此…大家都在努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:10:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚两人来庆祝吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都…会不会已经输了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦啦  到几回战了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四回战！自我新记录
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  和我一样呢  你很努力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是小一点的比赛  我可能就能进一线呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都打赢那个凯莉咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然二回战输掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也没关系  这是很大的进步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在一回战就输掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为对手是小珠嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  这个不用道歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还在…去洗手间了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生情况不容乐观啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段君  不好意思  我还不能输！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,场外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段君  我知道你努力过  也知道你有才能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我也有我的坚持
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持到今天的…坚持！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行不通的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效！段君从勇次君手里耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用擅长的抽胴做迷惑  来制造破绽！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就一比一了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也成长了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次君他  那么拼命…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打赢你的二刀流我是不甘心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好么  难得赢我一次  算得上扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再胜一场便是两胜两败  这样就才是扯平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会是二刀流
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛不是不能用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去看的武士电影用的是二刀流
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二刀流夺去了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要长大了在比赛中也是允许使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我是不会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦抓住了一样东西就永远不会放手的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是勇次赢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段君也真可惜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.06,0:14:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  就差一点了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次你成长了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打倒我的话  那你就没有敌人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取得优胜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一场和谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是凛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题！会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会为你加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放松哦  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:14:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都告诉她了吧  上段攻略法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时击中…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠你好厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离差了那么多  真是乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的小珠脑袋里可没有那些计算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样过会可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉碎战术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:15:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在可是高兴到不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她发现铃木凛是那种自己勉勉强强才能打中的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠她头一次尝到了挑战的甜头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手——！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手有效！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢  段君！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚小珠拿下一本了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想赢二刀流你还早了十年！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讲什么美国冷笑话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在中学的时候可也不是白混的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都那暴露无遗的斗争心  太赞啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都！笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:16:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么怪力…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a 「Power Of Love」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹部有效
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就一比一平
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下才是关键！小珠！加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方还有上段没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是关键时刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  她的剑道现在才要开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:54.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里所有的人  都喜欢剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道…好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比以前强太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人高兴  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我更不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌愈强  我愈强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.06,0:18:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的剑道！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了  你是用上段来对付我的上段
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想再来一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的建议派不上什么用场的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如果对方真的是你妈妈的话  你愿意输吗？」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是谁  我都想赢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是中段
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢上剑道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺——！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛结束！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！拿下第二本了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是原子火焰剑！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺击  一本
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜了  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这样就是一胜一败了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决胜局就留在下次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候变这么厉害了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠本来就厉害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去打了下延长战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:21:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就算是个人战的优胜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的饭碗算保住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管选择如何我都…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人出来负责的话  学校那边是说不过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿伸  我以后会怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.83,0:22:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心  我知道很多赚钱的活啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:22.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:27.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:34.13,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:55.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:02.22,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眠れない 月明かり ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:10.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前を ちらついてく 昼間の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:17.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分だけ 空回りで もどかしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:25.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目を閉じて  心の声  聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:32.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ知らない 私に出会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:40.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:47.95,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:22.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:27.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中闪耀着的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:34.13,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:55.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗边光着脚丫  仰望着夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:02.22,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有无法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:10.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮现出午时的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:17.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒劳得令人着急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:25.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}闭上眼睛倾听心中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:32.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然无法得知  它想与我相见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:40.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}光辉而耀眼的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:47.95,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.83,0:23:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿伸  这工作好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.98,0:23:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.89,0:23:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳动汗水会是甘甜的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.52,0:23:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿伸  摇得太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.99,0:24:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这船真能晃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.32,0:24:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  咽下去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.46,0:24:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是吐在海里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.36,0:24:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么虾兵蟹将的烦死你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.59,0:24:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！阿伸！是螃蟹！好可怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.85,0:24:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～小次郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.82,0:24:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回竹剑是最终话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.65,0:24:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「"自那以后"和"从今往后"」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.24,0:24:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自此往后能回家吗！？
